EXPRESSION: CASE WHEN COALESCE(IX_IXQDWLMT_1_0.CLOSED_DATE,'') <> ''  AND IX_IXQDWLMT_1_0.CLOSED_DATE <> '2069-12-31' THEN to_date(TRIM(IX_IXQDWLMT_1_0.CLOSED_DATE),'yyyy-MM-dd') WHEN IX_IXQDWLMT_1_0.CLOSED_DATE = '2069-12-31' THEN to_date('9999-12-31','yyyy-MM-dd') ELSE to_date('1000-01-03','yyyy-MM-DD') END
